<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Vocally - AI Product Descriptions for Shopify Stores</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #FF8C00;
      --dark-bg: #0a0a0a;
      --dark-secondary: #1a1a1a;
      --dark-tertiary: #2a2a2a;
      --text-primary: #ffffff;
      --text-secondary: #b0b0b0;
      --border: #333333;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      background: var(--dark-bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Header / Nav */
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.95);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-bottom-width: 2px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    nav {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo-nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-nav img {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 52px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .hero-content h1 .highlight {
      color: var(--primary);
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary);
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cta-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      border: 2px solid var(--primary);
    }

    .cta-primary:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .cta-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      border: 2px solid var(--primary);
      margin-left: 16px;
    }

    .cta-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-secondary) 0%, var(--dark-tertiary) 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 400px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-top: 2px solid var(--primary);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-visual::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--primary), transparent);
    }

    .hero-visual-content {
      font-size: 80px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .hero-visual-text {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* Stats */
    .stats {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .stat {
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 40px;
    }

    .stat::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 4px;
      height: 20px;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    /* How It Works */
    .how-it-works {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .section-header h2::before,
    .section-header h2::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
    }

    .section-header p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .step {
      padding: 30px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      background: var(--dark-secondary);
      position: relative;
    }

    .step:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(224, 70, 70, 0.2);
      background: var(--dark-tertiary);
    }

    .step::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .step:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(224, 70, 70, 0.3);
    }

    .step h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .step p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* Features Deep Dive */
    .features {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
      background: var(--dark-secondary);
    }

    .feature-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }

    .feature-row:nth-child(even) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      direction: rtl;
    }

    .feature-row:nth-child(even) > * {
      direction: ltr;
    }

    .feature-visual {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-tertiary) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 300px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 64px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .feature-visual::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(224, 70, 70, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .feature-content h3 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .feature-content h3::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--primary);
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .feature-content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .feature-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .feature-list li {
      padding: 8px 0;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .feature-list li:before {
      content: "▸";
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    /* Use Cases */
    .use-cases {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
    }

    .use-cases-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .use-case {
      padding: 40px;
      background: var(--dark-secondary);
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative;
    }

    .use-case::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      transform: scaleX(0);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
      transform-origin: left;
    }

    .use-case:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      background: var(--dark-tertiary);
    }

    .use-case:hover::before {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }

    .use-case-icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .use-case h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .use-case p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Pricing */
    .pricing {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
      background: var(--dark-secondary);
    }

    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }

    .pricing-card {
      background: var(--dark-tertiary);
      padding: 50px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative;
    }

    .pricing-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary) 0%, transparent 100%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .pricing-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(224, 70, 70, 0.2);
    }

    .pricing-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .pricing-card.featured {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(224, 70, 70, 0.1) 0%, rgba(224, 70, 70, 0.03) 100%);
    }

    .pricing-card.featured::before {
      opacity: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--primary));
    }

    .pricing-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .plan-name {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .plan-price {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .plan-price span {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .plan-description {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .plan-cta {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .plan-cta:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      border: 2px solid var(--primary);
      padding: 12px 22px;
    }

    .plan-features {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .plan-features li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .plan-features li:before {
      content: "▸";
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .plan-features li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .faq-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .faq-question {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .faq-question:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .faq-answer {
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* CTA Footer */
    .cta-footer {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 100px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--dark-secondary);
    }

    .cta-footer h2 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .cta-footer h2 .highlight {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .cta-footer p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      border-top: 2px solid var(--primary);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero,
      .stats,
      .steps,
      .use-cases-grid,
      .pricing-grid,
      .feature-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 42px;
      }

      nav ul {
        gap: 24px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero,
      .stats,
      nav,
      .how-it-works,
      .features,
      .use-cases,
      .pricing,
      .faq,
      .cta-footer,
      footer {
        padding-left: 20px;
        padding-right: 20px;
      }

      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      .cta-secondary {
        display: block;
        margin-left: 0;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .section-header h2 {
        font-size: 32px;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .section-header h2::before,
      .section-header h2::after {
        display: none;
      }

      .pricing-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="#" class="logo-nav">
        <span>Vocally</span>
      </a>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
        <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:sethkueker@gmail.com">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Stop writing product descriptions. <span class="highlight">Start generating them.</span></h1>
      <p>
        Vocally uses AI to create consistent, on-brand product descriptions for your entire Shopify catalog in minutes, not days.
      </p>
      <div>
        <a href="https://apps.shopify.com/vocally" class="cta-primary">Install from Shopify App Store</a>
        <a href="mailto:sethkueker@gmail.com" class="cta-secondary">Questions? Email us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-visual-content">📝</div>
        <div class="hero-visual-text">Generate 50+ descriptions in minutes</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">40 hrs</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Saved per month (per merchant)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">$1,200</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Cost of freelance alternatives</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">On-brand consistency</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Three steps to scale</h2>
      <p>From setup to finished descriptions in minutes</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3>Define your voice</h3>
        <p>Set your brand voice once. Tone, style, key selling points.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3>Pick products</h3>
        <p>Choose one product or your entire catalog to generate for.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3>Review & publish</h3>
        <p>Review descriptions, make edits if needed, save to Shopify.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <h3>Done</h3>
        <p>Your catalog now has consistent, compelling descriptions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Deep Dive -->
  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Built for merchants</h2>
      <p>Everything you need to scale descriptions without the headache</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-row">
      <div>
        <div class="feature-visual">🎯</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3>Brand voice control</h3>
        <p>
          Define your tone, style, and messaging once. Vocally applies it consistently across every description in your store — no matter how many products you have.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Custom tone and style</li>
          <li>Key features to highlight</li>
          <li>Reusable across entire catalog</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-row">
      <div>
        <div class="feature-visual">⚡</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3>Bulk generation</h3>
        <p>
          Generate descriptions for 50, 500, or 5,000 products at once. What would take weeks of manual writing happens in minutes.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Single or bulk generation</li>
          <li>Edit before publishing</li>
          <li>Instant save to Shopify</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-row">
      <div>
        <div class="feature-visual">✏️</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3>Always under your control</h3>
        <p>
          Descriptions are AI-generated, but human-reviewed. You see every description before it goes live. Edit, approve, or regenerate in seconds.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Preview before saving</li>
          <li>Edit any description</li>
          <li>Regenerate if needed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="use-cases">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Perfect for any business</h2>
      <p>Vocally works for dropshippers, B2B sellers, print-on-demand shops, and more</p>
    </div>
    <div class="use-cases-grid">
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case-icon">🏪</div>
        <h3>Dropshipping</h3>
        <p>Stop copy-pasting supplier descriptions. Generate branded descriptions that actually convert.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case-icon">🎨</div>
        <h3>Print-on-Demand</h3>
        <p>Quickly describe hundreds of customizable products without writing each one manually.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="use-case">
        <div class="use-case-icon">📦</div>
        <h3>High-volume sellers</h3>
        <p>Managing 1,000+ products? Generate consistent descriptions in a fraction of the time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Simple, transparent pricing</h2>
      <p>Start free. Upgrade when you need more.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="plan-name">Basic</div>
